playstore_details.description:
Lumi Wallet is a secure way to buy, store, exchange, and manage all your crypto in one place.

LUMI WALLET MAJOR FEATURES
1. Buy Bitcoin (BTC), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Ethereum (ETH), Tether USD (USDT), USD Coin (USDC), Dogecoin (DOGE) and more via debit or credit card.
2. Crypto to crypto exchange (1000+ coins and tokens).
3. Ethereum Wallet with mulptiple addresess.
4. Hierarchical Deterministic Bitcoin Wallet.
5. High-level security.
6. World-class UX/UI-design.
7. Global human support that cares 24/7.
8. Open source - our code is publicly available.

Lumi Crypto Wallet suits all your crypto needs!

BUY CRYPTOCURRENCY WITH YOUR CREDIT CARD
You can buy Bitcoin, Bitcoin Cash, Ethereum, Stablecoins, Defi (decentralized finance) tokens, and other crypto with a credit card: select the amount and add your card.

SUPPORTED CURRENCIES:
United States Dollar (USD), Australian Dollar (AUD), Canadian Dollar (CAD), Swiss franc (CHF), Euro (EUR), Pound sterling (GBP) and more.

ETHEREUM WALLET WITH MULTIPLE ADDRESSES
Create multiple Ethereum addresses for different transactions. You don't need to create a separate wallet to get a different address.

HIERARCHICAL DETERMINISTIC BITCOIN WALLET
Lumi Crypto Wallet creates a new bitcoin address for each new transaction, which greatly improves the privacy of your wallet.

HIGH-LEVEL SECURITY OF FUNDS
Security is a primary focus of our crypto wallet: private keys are kept exclusively on your device. All your crypto assets are protected with high level encryption and cryptography. All funds are held in cold storage and you always remain the sole owner of your cryptocurrency.

WORLD-CLASS UX/UI-DESIGN
We’ve created the most user-friendly cryptocurrency wallet. Maximum simplicity and consistency of each element is our mantra.

MULTI-CURRENCY & MULTI-TOKEN
You can use Lumi Wallet to send, receive, manage, and exchange Bitcoin, Ethereum, Bitcoin Cash, and more than 1000 ERC-20 tokens. Fixed exchange rates for more than 100+ pairs. Build your crypto portfolio without leaving your secure wallet with low fees and exchange within 15 minutes.

SUPPORTED CRYPTOCURRENCIES:
Bitcoin (BTC) Legacy + Bitcoin Segwit, Ethereum (ETH), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Dogecoin (DOGE)

EOS (EOS)
Binance (BNB)
Tether USD (USDT)
TrueUSD (TUSD)
USD Coin (USDC)
Bitcoin Gold (BTG)
Chainlink (LINK)
Basic Attention Token (BAT)
Paxos Standard Token (PAX)
Gemini Dollar (GUSD)
Compound (COMP) and more.

We are more than happy to get in touch with you via Telegram (@lumigroup) or Twitter (@Lumi_wallet) - drop us a line and let’s have a chat!
